def find_numeral_pairs(number: str) -> list[str]:
    letters = [chr(c) for c in range(ord('A'), ord(number) + 1)]
    num_index = ord(number) + ord('A')
    pairs = []
    for i in range(num_index // 2 + 1):
        pairs.append(f'{letters[i]} + {letters[num_index - i]}')
    return pairs
